title: Catch-Phrase Spouting Duo
content:
Team Rocket: "Looks like Team Rocket's blasting off again..." *ping*
• Of course, this has been lampshaded by now and variations aren't so unusual:

Jessie & Meowth: "Looks like Team Rocket's blasting off again..." *ping*

James (currently separated from his team-mates): "I could have sworn someone just screamed blasting off again, : "I could have sworn someone just screamed blasting off again, but we copyrighted that didn't we ? Oh well!"
